comments: Gasol (TOR) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Lopez (MIL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Leonard (TOR) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Gasol (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Middleton (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

LAR and LLB show Lopez (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by Leonard (TOR).  The ball is cleanly dislodged as Leonard loses control during his gather.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lowry (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lowry (TOR) removes his hand prior to Bledsoe's (MIL) gather and upward shooting motion on his drive.
RLB shows Siakam (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Antetokounmpo (MIL). Both players then make incidental contact during the rebound.
RLB shows Green (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Antetokounmpo (MIL) at the end of his drive.
Gasol (TOR) makes marginal contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) back during the rebound, but the contact does not affect his ability to naturally go for the ball.
Leonard (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Green (TOR) makes marginal contact to Bledsoe's (MIL) body during the drive, but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
RLB shows Gasol (TOR) makes contact to Bledsoe's (MIL) shoulder during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Gasol (TOR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) commits a take foul on Middleton (MIL).
Gasol (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bledsoe (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LAR shows Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) that doesn't affect his SQBR.
Hill (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lowry (TOR) and cleanly blocks the shot.
Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hill (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Replay confirms, Hill (MIL) wraps Green (TOR) and affects his SQBR before the ball is inbounded.
Gasol (TOR) makes marginal contact to Middleton's (MIL) arm and body, but the contact does not affect his ability to maintain possession of the ball.
Gasol (TOR) lifts his foot and makes a kicking motion when he contacts the basketball.
